title: Jai
subTitle: Jai, a young boy, witnesses the murder of his parents at the hands of their greedy manager. When he grows up, he sets out with his caretaker to avenge the wrongs done to his family.

title: Varusham 16
subTitle: Kannan, a teenager, falls in love with his uncle's daughter, Radhika, but things turn upside down when her grandmother disapproves of their relationship.

title: Kadhal Oviyam
subTitle: A village girl falls in love with an orphan with visual impairment. However, when her mother wishes her to marry a well-settled, she elopes with him.

title: Chinna Durai
subTitle: Chinnadurai, a village do-gooder, helps people in distress but earns the enmity of a fellow villager Ponnambalam. Later, Ponnambalam tries to poison Chinnadurai, but he survives.

title: Sundara Kandam
subTitle: Priya, a young student, falls in love with her teacher, a man who shows no interest in her. Complications arise when the professor gets married, and she continues to stir trouble in his life.

title: Bramma
subTitle: Ravivarman, a sketch artist, loses his beloved wife in a tragic flight accident. When he helps the police track a dangerous criminal, the miscreant vows to seek revenge on Ravivarman.

title: Kalam
subTitle: Captain Gopinath, along with Serina, the daughter of a Pakistani army general, must thwart Pakistan's plans of using a nuclear bomb against India.
